metadata.name: Kashchey the Immortal
metadata.description:
Artwork is inspired by Russian fairytale “Kashchey the Immortal”
Story tells that the death of Kashchey is hidden at the end of the needle, needle is in the egg, egg is in the duck. 

Audio track made by Pass Me The Sugar. Created by sampling the movie “Kashchey the Immortal” from 1945 year. 

Resolution: 1512x1890
